rows.label: tev999906_MSG2101
rows.name:
Ha! Of course you want support from my division!
I already filed the request![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999906_MSG3001

rows.label: tev999906_MSG3101
rows.name: Let's go then. I'd follow you anywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999906_MSG5001
rows.name: Sorry, but I'm on another job at the moment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999906_MSG5101
rows.name: Sorry, I can't pull myself away from this right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999906_MSG5102
rows.name: Try me again later, all right?[ST:wait ]
